node.text:
Today is my Birthday and I wanted to give back! I’m doing my OWN Raffle GIVE AWAY in 1 hour (12pm EST!!!) This Give away will be taking place on IG LIVE! All you have to do is show UP and show OUT! It’s our birthday so let’s Celebrate! Can’t wait to see all the winners❤️

.
RULES:
-Follow @YoungEzee (me)
-Tag your friends in this post
-Download Cashapp 

(All entries start at $1 on Cash app!! 12pm EST! When entering raffle, please put your raffle amount along side your IG handle and what item you’d like to Get, so I can choose you as a Winner. My cash app is $YoungEzee)

Example: “apple airpods @youngezee $$”

-Airpods $5 entry
-Canon cameras $10
-Gucci satchel $15
-iPhones $20 entry 
-Mac books $50 entry
-$2000 $100 entry

node.title: Happy Birthday to Me and YOU! 🤪
